channel.title: Crashing on Interloper
channel.description:
I've played without any issues, I died on the part where mind controllers spawn for the 2nd time on Interloper. I was able to reload an old save once but then I died on that one too. Now both of my saves wont load. Any ideas?
Edit: I dont get any error messages, just crashes to desktop.
